<doc id="581600" wikidata="Q1219644" url="?curid=581600" title="Malik Shah">
<text>Malik-Shah (), also transliterated as &quot;Malek-Shah&quot;, &quot;Malikshah&quot; or &quot;Melikshah&quot;, may refer to:

* Malik-Shah I (1055–1092), sultan of Great Seljuq
* Malik-Shah II (), grandson of Malik Shah I, sultan of Great Seljuq
* Malik-Shah III (1152–1153), sultan of Great Seljuq
* Malik Shah (Rûm) (1110–1116), sultan of the Seljuq Sultanate of Rûm</text><links>
