Webby Award

* &quot;John Lewis: Witness to History&quot; (Winner, 2021: People&#x27;s Choice Documentary in History) 

AIBs Award

* &quot;Solving for Zero&quot; (Winner, 2022: Science and Technology - TV/Video)

