*Gelatt, Roland, &quot;The Fabulous Phonograph&quot;. New York: Collier Books,1977.
*&quot;Sound Revolutions: a Biography of Fred Gaisberg, Founding Father of Commercial Sound Recording&quot;. London: Sanctuary, 1999 ( / ).

